      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOOLS RUSH IN (2) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when second (30.95) in a Grade 5 over 525m at this track. Safe beginner who should be prominent to the first bend. Will find this more suitable and can atone. SHE'S VICIOUS (3) went straight to the front and never headed when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 10 lengths at this track (31.41). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Can measure up this time. STOKER SMOKER (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (23.90) last time in a Grade 5 at Casino. The form out of last race has been strong. Cannot be taken lightly. OXLEY DREAM GIRL (7) will make her presence felt following a brief layoff.",
